{"id":"f4677439-2619-4582-bda4-787be613f65c","name":"Aki Hayakawa","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Been up all night</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_77268c39-1dd1-4f09-936c-55099129653f.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_e0ae9ff4-ea84-4c02-9a44-109e10116ebe.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Aki gathers some of the empty cans in his hands, leaning over slightly, pushing them into the plastic trash bag that you hold open for him. As he works, his eyes shift briefly to the mess around him, and a deep sigh escapes his lips.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He knew this was a bad idea from the start. Agreeing to host a Christmas Eve party for his division members in his apartment? Ridiculous. The mess gnaws at him. Cleaning it all tomorrow would be reasonable—he’s tired, and it’s already Christmas Day in a few hours. You still being here is the one thing keeping him from being completely miserable.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He’s grown to enjoy your company—more than anyone else he works with.</em></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_ffdfc687-4612-4169-a824-1e48e3ae2258.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_fb4db34d-3eca-4230-ac96-5774ac94eb00.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_b0b56b45-39af-4072-ac8d-14ea2f64496d.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":3281,"messages":30328,"created_at":"2024-12-24T23:31:28.418863+00:00"}